            "text": "At the same time, Democratic partisans seem blissfully ignorant of the pervasive economic desperation in America — the very kind that has been present during those dark moments of history when fascism reared its ugly head.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "These partisans seem wholly unconcerned about their party’s lethargy in Washington, happy to smugly insinuate that those expecting a check don’t understand the legislative process and don’t understand that $1,400 is actually $2,000, even though it most certainly is not. They somehow still believe that word-parsing “well, actually” op-eds and tweets and MSNBC roundtables will satiate millions of people who were told to expect help but haven’t gotten any.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "All is not lost. There is still time to fix things. There is still a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "legislative maneuver",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.ajc.com/news/nation-world/schumer-democrats-might-invoke-14th-amendment-to-bar-trump-if-senate-acquits/PCP67ZMZYZHV7FG5JFG3O42ZTE/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " potentially available to hold Trump accountable. And those survival checks still can be sent out right now, if Democrats get serious. And the good news is that at least a few progressives in Congress seem to understand how dire and urgent the situation has become.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/JamaalBowmanNY/status/1360607012111978497",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/JamaalBowmanNY/status/1360607012111978497\"></a></blockquote><script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "But make no mistake about it: We are now at the turning point. This movie will either become an inspirational story of fighting through adversity to change our course and achieve a better future. Or it will become a nihilistic horror show.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We are not in the theater watching from a distance. We are not streaming this on Netflix from the safety and comfort of our homes. We are all characters in this story. We all have a role to play and we all have to choose whether to be protagonists fighting for a better democratic future or antagonists allowing partisan tribalism to facilitate the rise of fascism.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It’s time to choose which side you are on. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Choose wisely",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
